# Icons Directory

Place application icons here:

- `app-icon.ico` - Windows icon
- `app-icon.icns` - macOS icon
- `app-icon.png` - Linux icon (512x512)
- `tray-idle.png` - System tray icon (idle state)
- `tray-listening.png` - System tray icon (listening state)
- `tray-speaking.png` - System tray icon (speaking state)

Icon specifications:

- Windows ICO: 256x256, 128x128, 64x64, 48x48, 32x32, 16x16
- macOS ICNS: 1024x1024, 512x512, 256x256, 128x128, 64x64, 32x32, 16x16
- PNG: 512x512 (transparent background)
